metadata.name: Canopy Surfer
metadata.description:
My friend Cristobal is surfing the forest canopy on a Macaw feather

...::: About the Collection :::...
In this collection I use Artificial Intelligence (AI) to reimagine my trip to the "Madre de Dios" region in the Peruvian Amazon. The artworks have surreal elements inspired by what I personally saw during my stay, including the jungle, rivers, lakes, wonderful animals and even friends.
